NOTE ON THE VOCABULARY DATA (words_cs.js)

The computer-science term definitions bundled in words_cs.js are ORIGINAL
educational content, written from scratch to align with the CIE 9618
Computer Science teaching scope. They are NOT reproduced from, and contain
no copyrighted material owned by, any examination board or textbook
publisher. This vocabulary data is released under the same MIT terms above
and may be freely used, shared and adapted.
